Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Hayden Ferry Lakeside is a mixed-use project consisting of 1.6 million SF of office, retail & residential. Located in the heart of Downtown Tempe, providing excellent freeway access via Loop 202 & 101. 

Hayden Ferry Lakesides central location is ideal for commuters from across the Valley  with nearby access to all the major Phoenix Freeways, Light Rail, city-wide bus service and is just minutes from Sky Harbor International Airport, one of the busiest airports in the world. Tempe is a workforce importer, with approximately 210,000 people employed in a city of just 161,000 residents.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: One Hundred Mill positioned in a signature location along Mill Avenue in Downtown Tempe, affords emerging generations of office users the broad appeal of a modernly designed building in a bustling job sector. Located within a tech-centric corridor, One Hundred Mill will be a pivotal point of reference in Downtown Tempe as current corporations expand their presence and a burgeoning influx of out-of-state users relocate to Greater Phoenix. Designed with todays tenants in mind, the project will incorporate natural light with extensive glass lines on large, flexible footplates that can accommodate office users who appreciate the true Class A office experience.
